                        <h2 class="mb-4">About Us</h2>
                        <p>Welcome to Thistle Triangle, where the rich culinary traditions of Europe and Asia come together to create an unforgettable dining experience. Located in the heart of Kathmandu, we are proud to offer a diverse menu that celebrates the flavors, spices, and ingredients from across two vibrant continents.<br><br>At Thistle Triangle, we believe that food is more than just nourishment—it’s a celebration of culture and connection. Founded in 2018, our mission has always been to bring people together through the universal language of delicious food. Drawing inspiration from the bustling markets of Istanbul, the aromatic spice trails of Central Asia, and the refined culinary techniques of Europe, we offer a menu that’s as diverse as our roots.<br><br>Our dishes are a harmonious blend of East and West, where bold Asian spices meet European elegance. Whether it’s our savory dumplings, hearty stews, delicate pastries, or freshly grilled meats, each dish is thoughtfully crafted using the finest locally sourced and imported ingredients. Vegetarian and vegan options are also available, ensuring everyone can enjoy the best of Eurasian cuisine. <br>
                        <p>Step into Thistle Triangle and be transported to a warm, inviting space that reflects our fusion of cultures. With décor inspired by both traditional and modern Eurasian aesthetics, we aim to create a welcoming atmosphere where you can relax, savor your meal, and create lasting memories with friends and family.</p>
                        <p>We are dedicated to providing exceptional service and a memorable dining experience. Whether you’re joining us for a casual lunch, a romantic dinner, or a special celebration, our team is here to ensure every detail is perfect.Come and explore the unique blend of flavors that define Thistle Triangle. We can’t wait to share our passion for Eurasian cuisine with you.</p>
